<author>ʿṣạm ṣbḥy, sạmḥ ʿbyd</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- jạy wʿsẖmạn fy mḥbtk tqblny
 jạy tạny lrḥmtk tstrny
 tạny jạy lnʿmtk tgẖfr ly
 ạlqrạr- sạmḥny sạmḥny wạqblny
 ạstrny ṭhrny wạgẖfr ly
 yạ ạ̉bwyạ yạlly btḥbny rạjʿ lk
 2- knt mạsk fy ạ̹ydyk wsybtk
 yạmạ qlt ạ̹n ạ̉nạ lyk wkẖntk
 qlt ḥby yạ rby lyk wbʿtk
 3- tht rḥt nbsẖt ậbạr mạ btrwy</lyrics>
<title>jạy wʿsẖmạn</title>
</song>